        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Natural Features Near The Valley",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_127685_000024_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/127685/596_127685_000024_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "In the basin of the Illilouette there are sixteen, in the Tenaya basin and its branches thirteen, in the Yosemite Creek basin fourteen, and in the Pohono or Bridal Veil one, making a grand total of one hundred and eleven lakes whose waters come to sing at Yosemite.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_127685_000026_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/127685/596_127685_000026_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Down The Yosemite Creek",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_127685_000028_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/127685/596_127685_000028_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "The total descent made by the stream from its highest sources to its confluence with the Merced in the Valley is about six thousand feet, while the distance is only about ten miles, an average fall of six hundred feet per mile.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000002_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000002_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Their only pet was a dog named Shiro, and on him they lavished all the affection of their old age.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000002_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000002_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Indeed, they loved him so much that whenever they had anything nice to eat they denied themselves to give it to Shiro.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000002_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000002_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Now Shiro means \"white,\" and he was so called because of his color.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000003_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000003_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Sure enough, Shiro was waiting for his master and the evening tit bit.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000005_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000005_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "He ran back to the house, fetched his spade and began to dig the ground at that spot.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000009_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000009_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "He then took his spade and hastened to his own field, forcing the unwilling Shiro to follow him.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000010_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000010_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "You must find them for me!",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000010_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000010_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Where are they? Where?",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000010_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000010_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Where?\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-normal_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "high",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000013_000004",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000013_000004.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "He seized his spade, and with all his strength struck Shiro and killed him on the spot.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-low",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "low"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000013_000006",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000013_000006.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Then he returned to the house, telling no one, not even his wife, what he had done.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000015_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000015_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Out of the trunk he made a mortar.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000017_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000017_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "They tasted the cakes and found them nicer than any other food.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000023_000003",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000023_000003.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "Now please give me the ashes of the mortar, as I wish to keep them in remembrance of my dog.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-normal_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "normal",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000028_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000028_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "This Knight told him that he was a retainer of a great Daimio (Earl); that one of the favorite cherry trees in this nobleman's garden had withered, and that though every one in his service had tried all manner of means to revive it, none took effect. The Knight was sore perplexed when he saw what great displeasure the loss of his favorite cherry tree caused the Daimio.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000029_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000029_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "\"And,\" added the Knight, \"I shall be very much obliged if you will come at once.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000036_000001",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000036_000001.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "I shall look on.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000040_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000040_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "The Daimio ordered that henceforth the old man should call himself by the name of Hana Saka Jijii, or \"The Old Man who makes the Trees to Blossom,\" and that henceforth all were to recognize him by this name, and he sent him home with great honor.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000050_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000050_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "\"Yes, my Lord!\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000051_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000051_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "\"That is strange!\" said the Daimio.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "normal"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000052_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000052_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "\"I am the true Hana Saka Jijii.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "fast",
        "energy": "very high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000055_000000",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000055_000000.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "But not only did the tree not burst into flower, but not even a bud came forth.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000055_000002",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000055_000002.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "But all to no effect.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "very low",
        "speed": "slow",
        "energy": "high"
    },
    {
        "item_name": "LibriTTS_R-596_139612_000055_000005",
        "wav_path": "/apdcephfs_qy3/share_1474453/shuoyizhou/data_preprocess/LibriTTS-R/LibriTTS_R/596/139612/596_139612_000055_000005.wav",
        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-596",
        "content": "From this imprisonment the wicked old man was never freed. Thus did he meet with punishment at last for all his evil doings.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-low_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "low",
        "speed": "very slow",
